The paper presents an approach for the verification of feed-forward neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The focus is on networks with piece-wise linear activation functions, which is a specific aspect of neural networks that falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The approach also involves the use of a specialized verification algorithm and search process, which can be seen as a form of control theory or system analysis (cs.SY).
